fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n一定會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好掛住佢</blockquote><br />\n唔好咁肉酸啦，拍多幾次拖，比人飛多幾次就無乜感覺，唔係話你唔愛佢，但每個人一開頭分手都係咁，叫生叫死，幾年後望返你會覺得而家好戇鳩，因為你已經攬緊另一個，而佢都係</blockquote><br />\n諗左已經認定佢係最後一個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁之前就唔會堅持分手啦on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"808a3ae81c2a83354fa945e55b9e5841b507eb2b","tid":381222,"uid":33565,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T17:45:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>好驚佢就係咁俾人追左<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n一定會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好掛住佢</blockquote><br />\n唔好咁肉酸啦，拍多幾次拖，比人飛多幾次就無乜感覺，唔係話你唔愛佢，但每個人一開頭分手都係咁，叫生叫死，幾年後望返你會覺得而家好戇鳩，因為你已經攬緊另一個，而佢都係</blockquote><br />\n諗左已經認定佢係最後一個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n第一次分手，個個都話自己以後唔再拍拖，醒下啦，冇尊嚴既人狗也不屌</blockquote><br />\n有幾無尊嚴?</blockquote><br />\n睇哂成個post自己講過乜野，老實講戀就係人都失過，你呢種就一定復合無望，因為連我地外人都睇唔起你"},{"pid":"862ed628114821dcc14e67eb4400ed9a9e1ba101","tid":381222,"uid":46758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T20:56:22.000Z","msg":"你自己話分手 又後悔"},{"pid":"28618a5fda2b4ad54fb2a53fbf170b7a4e9f7b19","tid":381222,"uid":4746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T22:42:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>屌你老母係到叫春有撚用咩<br />\n睇完尷尬到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n叫下春 忍住唔chur佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"380f04c352f43806904889cc42f1642107a19a17","tid":381222,"uid":4746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T00:58:39.000Z","msg":"謝謝大家 我而家會重新做人 <br />\n做好自己 追返佢<br />\n追返之前 俾人追左 都希望佢有幸福"},{"pid":"3a7ab5bb000094f36a69dd5f9e72a54976777aa3","tid":381222,"uid":76812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T01:04:33.000Z","msg":"抵撚你死，扮咩撚高竇"},{"pid":"f165b7dd85745e0b26b16f8492f87ea868deb76a","tid":381222,"uid":106967,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T02:01:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>屌你老母係到叫春有撚用咩<br />\n睇完尷尬到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n叫下春 忍住唔chur佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n抒發下係好事"},{"pid":"1d1c35a42ba21d8d8b79f2c4050e6493bb99d894","tid":381222,"uid":126698,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T02:30:40.000Z","msg":"樓主 變左質就係變左架啦<br />\ntiming唔岩<br />\n就算一齊返 都唔會返到以前咁<br />\n佢對你決絕啲反而仲好<br />\n一開始好痛好痛 時間幫到你<br />\n預期挽救一段有缺憾既感情<br />\n不如增值自己 重新出發"},{"pid":"5930424b335211fc2cd6c444c1ace379fc48fa69","tid":381222,"uid":125966,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T03:11:55.000Z","msg":"再chur你個ex只會愈黎愈反感<br />\n其實你都唔會想係佢心目中變成一個討厭既人<br />\n試過朋友個ex散左之後幾個月都瘋狂打電話比佢<br />\n佢本身由無乜野都變到對個ex超反感<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果你係你口中咁愛佢 就更加唔應該騷擾佢<br />\n或者勉勉做返朋友 難為自己又難為人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你都唔會想一個你愛過既人變到咁憎你<br />\n分左手本應就變返做兩條平行線 唔好再打擾對方<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n樓主真係諗通就好 唔好再逼你個ex<br />\n為左佢變得更好已經夠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n要返黎既最後都會返黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"570217029d048cab7d18063b8a4bf5ab93a87b74","tid":381222,"uid":4746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T08:17:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>樓主 變左質就係變左架啦<br />\ntiming唔岩<br />\n就算一齊返 都唔會返到以前咁<br />\n佢對你決絕啲反而仲好<br />\n一開始好痛好痛 時間幫到你<br />\n預期挽救一段有缺憾既感情<br />\n不如增值自己 重新出發</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<blockquote>再chur你個ex只會愈黎愈反感<br />\n其實你都唔會想係佢心目中變成一個討厭既人<br />\n試過朋友個ex散左之後幾個月都瘋狂打電話比佢<br />\n佢本身由無乜野都變到對個ex超反感<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果你係你口中咁愛佢 就更加唔應該騷擾佢<br />\n或者勉勉做返朋友 難為自己又難為人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你都唔會想一個你愛過既人變到咁憎你<br />\n分左手本應就變返做兩條平行線 唔好再打擾對方<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n樓主真係諗通就好 唔好再逼你個ex<br />\n為左佢變得更好已經夠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n要返黎既最後都會返黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nThanks 兩位"}]}